{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1800,"text":"Mia Birdsong: Why is Black Lives Matter\nimportant for the US right now"},{"time":6400,"text":"and in the world?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":8560,"text":"Patrisse Cullors: Black Lives Matter\nis our call to action."},{"time":12440,"text":"It is a tool to reimagine a world"},{"time":16720,"text":"where black people are free to exist,"},{"time":19960,"text":"free to live."},{"time":21920,"text":"It is a tool for our allies\nto show up differently for us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":26160,"text":"I grew up in a neighborhood\nthat was heavily policed."},{"time":30480,"text":"I witnessed my brothers and my siblings"},{"time":34200,"text":"continuously stopped and frisked\nby law enforcement."},{"time":37960,"text":"I remember my home being raided."},{"time":40520,"text":"And one of my questions\nas a child was, why?"},{"time":44440,"text":"Why us?"},{"time":46360,"text":"Black Lives Matter\noffers answers to the why."},{"time":51600,"text":"It offers a new vision\nfor young black girls around the world"},{"time":57400,"text":"that we deserve to be fought for,"},{"time":60360,"text":"that we deserve to call\non local governments to show up for us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":67360,"text":"Opal Tometi: And antiblack racism --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":69120,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":72360,"text":"And antiblack racism is not only\nhappening in the United States."},{"time":76400,"text":"It's actually happening\nall across the globe."},{"time":79160,"text":"And what we need now more than ever\nis a human rights movement"},{"time":83320,"text":"that challenges systemic racism\nin every single context."}]},{"cues":[{"time":88200,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":92240,"text":"We need this because the global reality"},{"time":95800,"text":"is that black people\nare subject to all sorts of disparities"},{"time":101240,"text":"in most of our most challenging\nissues of our day."},{"time":105040,"text":"I think about issues like climate change,"},{"time":107840,"text":"and how six of the 10 worst impacted\nnations by climate change"},{"time":113360,"text":"are actually on the continent of Africa."},{"time":117080,"text":"People are reeling\nfrom all sorts of unnatural disasters,"},{"time":121800,"text":"displacing them\nfrom their ancestral homes"},{"time":124640,"text":"and leaving them without a chance\nat making a decent living."}]},{"cues":[{"time":128840,"text":"We also see disasters\nlike Hurricane Matthew,"},{"time":132920,"text":"which recently wreaked havoc\nin many different nations,"},{"time":136480,"text":"but caused the most damage to Haiti."},{"time":139800,"text":"Haiti is the poorest country\nin this hemisphere,"},{"time":144040,"text":"and its inhabitants are black people."},{"time":147880,"text":"And what we're seeing in Haiti"},{"time":149760,"text":"is that they were actually facing\na number of challenges"},{"time":152960,"text":"that even preceded this hurricane."},{"time":155680,"text":"They were reeling from the earthquake,"},{"time":157560,"text":"they were reeling from cholera\nthat was brought in by UN peacekeepers"},{"time":161760,"text":"and still hasn't been eradicated."},{"time":164560,"text":"This is unconscionable."},{"time":166720,"text":"And this would not happen if this nation\ndidn't have a population that was black,"},{"time":172640,"text":"and we have to be real about that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":175040,"text":"But what's most heartening right now"},{"time":177240,"text":"is that despite these challenges,"},{"time":179440,"text":"what we're seeing is\nthat there's a network of Africans"},{"time":182440,"text":"all across the continent"},{"time":184080,"text":"who are rising up and fighting back\nand demanding climate justice."}]},{"cues":[{"time":188280,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":191840,"text":"MB: So Alicia,"},{"time":193080,"text":"you've said that when\nblack people are free,"},{"time":195880,"text":"everyone is free."},{"time":197840,"text":"Can you talk about what that means?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":199560,"text":"Alicia Garza: Sure."},{"time":200800,"text":"So I think race and racism\nis probably the most studied"},{"time":204760,"text":"social, economic and political\nphenomenon in this country,"},{"time":208680,"text":"but it's also the least understood."},{"time":211840,"text":"The reality is that race\nin the United States"},{"time":214640,"text":"operates on a spectrum\nfrom black to white."},{"time":217600,"text":"Doesn't mean that people who are\nin between don't experience racism,"},{"time":222000,"text":"but it means that the closer\nyou are to white on that spectrum,"},{"time":225880,"text":"the better off you are."},{"time":227200,"text":"And the closer to black\nthat you are on that spectrum"},{"time":230200,"text":"the worse off your are."},{"time":232040,"text":"When we think about\nhow we address problems in this country,"},{"time":235880,"text":"we often start from a place\nof trickle-down justice."},{"time":239640,"text":"So using white folks\nas the control we say,"},{"time":242480,"text":"well, if we make things\nbetter for white folks"},{"time":244647,"text":"then everybody else is going to get free."},{"time":247440,"text":"But actually it doesn't work that way."},{"time":249320,"text":"We have to address problems at the root,"},{"time":252000,"text":"and when you deal with what's\nhappening in black communities,"},{"time":256160,"text":"it creates an effervescence, right?"},{"time":258519,"text":"So a bubble up rather than a trickle down."},{"time":261360,"text":"Let me give an example."},{"time":263120,"text":"When we talk about the wage gap,"},{"time":264720,"text":"we often say women make 78 cents\nto every dollar that a man makes."},{"time":270240,"text":"You all have heard that before."},{"time":272120,"text":"But those are the statistics\nfor white women and white men."},{"time":275360,"text":"The reality is that black women\nmake something like 64 cents"},{"time":279480,"text":"to every 78 cents that white women make."},{"time":282960,"text":"When we talk about latinas,\nit goes down to about 58 cents."},{"time":287040,"text":"If we were to talk about indigenous women,"},{"time":289160,"text":"if we were to talk about trans women,"},{"time":291000,"text":"it would even go further down."},{"time":292920,"text":"So again,"},{"time":294160,"text":"if you deal with those\nwho are the most impacted,"},{"time":296560,"text":"everybody has an opportunity\nto benefit from that,"},{"time":299840,"text":"rather than dealing with the folks\nwho are not as impacted,"},{"time":303880,"text":"and expecting it to trickle down."}]},{"cues":[{"time":306120,"text":"MB: So I love the effervescence,"},{"time":307720,"text":"bubbling up."}]},{"cues":[{"time":308960,"text":"AG: Effervescence -- like champagne."}]},{"cues":[{"time":310720,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":311960,"text":"MB: Who doesn't love\na glass of champagne, right?"},{"time":314320,"text":"Champagne and freedom, right?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":315760,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":317040,"text":"What more could we want, y'all?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":319320,"text":"So you all have been\ndoing this for a minute,"},{"time":322280,"text":"and the last few years have been --"},{"time":325680,"text":"well, I can't even imagine,"},{"time":327040,"text":"but I'm sure very transformative."},{"time":329440,"text":"And I know that you all\nhave learned a lot about leadership."},{"time":333480,"text":"What do you want\nto share with these people"},{"time":335560,"text":"about what you've learned\nabout leadership?"},{"time":337640,"text":"Patrisse, let's start with you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":339160,"text":"PC: Yeah, we have to invest\nin black leadership."},{"time":341760,"text":"That's what I've learned the most\nin the last few years."}]},{"cues":[{"time":344440,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":346800,"text":"What we've seen is thousands\nof black people showing up for our lives"},{"time":352800,"text":"with very little infrastructure\nand very little support."},{"time":357400,"text":"I think our work as movement leaders\nisn't just about our own visibility"},{"time":362720,"text":"but rather how do we\nmake the whole visible."},{"time":367360,"text":"How do we not just fight\nfor our individual selves"},{"time":370480,"text":"but fight for everybody?"},{"time":372320,"text":"And I also think"},{"time":375680,"text":"leadership looks like\neverybody in this audience"},{"time":380960,"text":"showing up for black lives."},{"time":383800,"text":"It's not just about coming\nand watching people on a stage, right?"},{"time":388040,"text":"It's about how do you\nbecome that leader --"},{"time":390064,"text":"whether it's in your workplace,\nwhether it's in your home --"},{"time":394200,"text":"and believe that the movement\nfor black lives isn't just for us,"},{"time":398280,"text":"but it's for everybody."}]},{"cues":[{"time":401480,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":405000,"text":"MB: What about you, Opal?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":406640,"text":"OT: So I've been learning\na great deal about interdependence."},{"time":410440,"text":"I've been learning\nabout how to trust your team."},{"time":414400,"text":"I've come up with this new mantra"},{"time":416040,"text":"after coming back\nfrom a three-month sabbatical,"},{"time":418800,"text":"which is rare for black women to take\nwho are in leadership,"},{"time":422480,"text":"but I felt it was really important\nfor my leadership and for my team"},{"time":426880,"text":"to also practice stepping back"},{"time":429520,"text":"as well as also sometimes stepping in."},{"time":432360,"text":"And what I learned in this process\nwas that we need to acknowledge"},{"time":437360,"text":"that different people\ncontribute different strengths,"},{"time":441080,"text":"and that in order\nfor our entire team to flourish,"},{"time":444600,"text":"we have to allow them\nto share and allow them to shine."},{"time":448760,"text":"And so during my sabbatical"},{"time":450480,"text":"with the organization\nthat I also work with,"},{"time":453080,"text":"I saw our team rise up in my absence."},{"time":456320,"text":"They were able to launch new programs,"},{"time":458800,"text":"fundraise."},{"time":460240,"text":"And when I came back,"},{"time":461960,"text":"I had to give them\na lot of gratitude and praise"},{"time":466040,"text":"because they showed me\nthat they truly had my back"},{"time":469800,"text":"and that they truly had their own backs."}]},{"cues":[{"time":472720,"text":"You know, in this process\nof my sabbatical,"},{"time":475360,"text":"I was really reminded"},{"time":476640,"text":"of this Southern African\nphilosophy of Ubuntu."},{"time":481600,"text":"I am because you are;"},{"time":484720,"text":"you are because I am."},{"time":487120,"text":"And I realized that my own leadership,"},{"time":490560,"text":"and the contributions\nthat I'm able to make,"},{"time":493120,"text":"is in large part due to the contributions\nthat they make, right?"},{"time":497400,"text":"And I have to acknowledge that,\nand I have to see that,"},{"time":500040,"text":"and so my new mantra is,\n\"Keep calm and trust the team.\""},{"time":504400,"text":"And also,"},{"time":505640,"text":"\"Keep calm and thank the team.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":508080,"text":"MB: You know, one of the things\nI feel like I've heard"},{"time":510680,"text":"in the context of the Black Lives Matter\nmovement more than anywhere else"},{"time":514480,"text":"is about being a leaderful movement,"},{"time":516720,"text":"and that's such a beautiful concept,"},{"time":518480,"text":"and I think that something"},{"time":519760,"text":"that women often bring\nto the conversation about leadership"},{"time":522600,"text":"is really the collective piece."},{"time":524120,"text":"What about you, Alicia?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":526040,"text":"AG: Yeah ..."},{"time":528000,"text":"How many of you heard that saying\nthat leadership is lonely?"},{"time":533400,"text":"I think that there is an element\nwhere leadership is lonely,"},{"time":536320,"text":"but I also believe\nthat it doesn't have to be like that."},{"time":539560,"text":"And in order for us to get to that point,"},{"time":542040,"text":"I think there's a few things\nthat we need to be doing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":544800,"text":"So one is we have to stop\ntreating leaders like superheroes."},{"time":549240,"text":"We are ordinary people\nattempting to do extraordinary things,"},{"time":554600,"text":"and so we need to be\nsupported in that way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":557680,"text":"The other thing that\nI've learned about leadership"},{"time":560440,"text":"is that there's a difference\nbetween leadership and celebrities, right?"},{"time":566640,"text":"And there's a way in which we've been\nkind of transformed into celebrities"},{"time":572000,"text":"rather than people\nwho are trying to solve a problem."},{"time":575840,"text":"And the way that we treat\ncelebrities is very fickle, right?"},{"time":578800,"text":"We like them one day,"},{"time":580080,"text":"we don't like what they're\nwearing the next day,"},{"time":582360,"text":"and all of a sudden we have issues, right?"},{"time":584680,"text":"So we need to stop deifying leaders"},{"time":587080,"text":"so that more people\nwill step into leadership."},{"time":589720,"text":"Lots of people are terrified\nto step into leadership"},{"time":592360,"text":"because of how much scrutiny they receive"},{"time":595080,"text":"and how brutal we are with leaders."}]},{"cues":[{"time":598200,"text":"And then the last thing\nthat I've learned about leadership"},{"time":600960,"text":"is that it's really easy to be a leader\nwhen everybody likes you."},{"time":605280,"text":"But it's hard to be a leader\nwhen you have to make hard choices"},{"time":609960,"text":"and when you have to do what's right,"},{"time":611840,"text":"even though people\nare not going to like you for it."},{"time":614760,"text":"And so in that way,"},{"time":616040,"text":"I think another way\nthat we can support leaders"},{"time":618400,"text":"is to struggle with us,"},{"time":621120,"text":"but struggle with us politically,"},{"time":622760,"text":"not personally."},{"time":624520,"text":"We can have disagreements\nwithout being disagreeable,"},{"time":628440,"text":"but it's important for us\nto sharpen each other,"},{"time":631640,"text":"so that we all can rise."}]},{"cues":[{"time":633280,"text":"MB: That's beautiful, thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":634853,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":639720,"text":"So you all are doing work"},{"time":642600,"text":"that forces you to face\nsome brutal, painful realities"},{"time":647320,"text":"on a daily basis."},{"time":650320,"text":"What gives you hope"},{"time":651800,"text":"and inspires you in that context?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":655320,"text":"PC: I am hopeful for black futures."},{"time":658320,"text":"And I say that because\nwe live in a society"},{"time":662560,"text":"that's so obsessed with black death."},{"time":665240,"text":"We have images of our death\non the TV screen,"},{"time":669840,"text":"on our Twitter timelines,"},{"time":671760,"text":"on our Facebook timelines,"},{"time":674320,"text":"but what if instead\nwe imagine black life?"},{"time":678320,"text":"We imagine black people\nliving and thriving."},{"time":681720,"text":"And that --"},{"time":683200,"text":"that inspires me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":687120,"text":"OT: What inspires me\nthese days are immigrants."},{"time":691640,"text":"Immigrants all over the world\nwho are doing the best that they can"},{"time":696280,"text":"to make a living,\nto survive and also to thrive."},{"time":700760,"text":"Right now there are\nover 244 million people"},{"time":704040,"text":"who aren't living\nin their country of origin."},{"time":707120,"text":"This is a 40 percent increase\nsince the year 2000."},{"time":711440,"text":"So what this tells me"},{"time":713120,"text":"is that the disparities across the globe\nare only getting worse."},{"time":718360,"text":"Yet there are people who are finding\nthe strength and wherewithal to travel,"},{"time":723640,"text":"to move,"},{"time":724880,"text":"to eke out a better living for themselves"},{"time":727200,"text":"and to provide for their families\nand their loved ones."},{"time":730440,"text":"And some of these people\nwho are immigrants"},{"time":733000,"text":"are also undocumented."},{"time":735000,"text":"They're unauthorized."},{"time":736720,"text":"And they inspire me even more"},{"time":738880,"text":"because although our society\nis telling them, you're not wanted,"},{"time":742640,"text":"you're not needed here,"},{"time":744040,"text":"and they're highly vulnerable\nand subject to abuse, to wage theft,"},{"time":748440,"text":"to exploitation and xenophobic attacks,"},{"time":751720,"text":"many of them are also beginning\nto organize in their communities."},{"time":755920,"text":"And what I'm seeing is\nthat there's also an emerging network"},{"time":760120,"text":"of black, undocumented people\nwho are resisting the framework,"},{"time":764440,"text":"and resisting the criminalization\nof their existence."},{"time":767400,"text":"And that to me is incredibly powerful"},{"time":770000,"text":"and inspires me every singe day."}]},{"cues":[{"time":772320,"text":"MB: Thank you."},{"time":774680,"text":"Alicia?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":777120,"text":"AG: So we know that young people\nare the present and the future,"},{"time":781160,"text":"but what inspires me are older people"},{"time":784600,"text":"who are becoming transformed\nin the service of this movement."},{"time":789320,"text":"We all know that as you get older,"},{"time":791000,"text":"you get a little more\nentrenched in your ways."},{"time":793200,"text":"It's happening to me, I know that's right."},{"time":796000,"text":"But I'm so inspired when I see people\nwho have a way that they do things,"},{"time":800800,"text":"have a way that they\nthink about the world,"},{"time":802880,"text":"and they're courageous enough to be open\nto listening to what the experiences are"},{"time":808320,"text":"of so many of us who want\nto live in world that's just"},{"time":811760,"text":"and want to live\nin a world that's equitable."},{"time":814360,"text":"And I'm also inspired by the actions\nthat I'm seeing older people taking"},{"time":819040,"text":"in service of this movement."},{"time":820600,"text":"I'm inspired by seeing older people\nstep into their own power and leadership"},{"time":825480,"text":"and say, \"I'm not passing a torch,"},{"time":828280,"text":"I'm helping you light the fire.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":831240,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":832480,"text":"MB: I love that --"},{"time":833720,"text":"yes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":835120,"text":"So in terms of action,"},{"time":837360,"text":"I think that it is awesome to sit here\nand be able to listen to you all,"},{"time":841800,"text":"and to have our minds open and shift,"},{"time":846080,"text":"but that's not going to get\nblack people free."},{"time":849080,"text":"So if you had one thing\nyou would like this audience"},{"time":852560,"text":"and the folks who are watching\naround the world to actually do,"},{"time":856280,"text":"what would that be?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":859720,"text":"AG: OK, two quick ones."},{"time":863120,"text":"One, call the White House."},{"time":865040,"text":"The water protectors\nare being forcibly removed"},{"time":869320,"text":"from the camp that they have set up\nto defend what keeps us alive."},{"time":874920,"text":"And that is intricately\nrelated to black lives."},{"time":877800,"text":"So definitely call the White House\nand demand that they stop doing that."},{"time":881880,"text":"There are tanks"},{"time":883120,"text":"and police officers arresting\nevery single person there as we speak."}]},{"cues":[{"time":888280,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":890880,"text":"The second thing that you can do"},{"time":895000,"text":"is to join something."},{"time":898360,"text":"Be a part of something."},{"time":899720,"text":"There are groups, collectives --"},{"time":902240,"text":"doesn't have to be a non-profit,\nyou know what I mean?"},{"time":904840,"text":"But there are groups that are doing\nwork in our communities right now"},{"time":908440,"text":"to make sure that black lives matter\nso all lives matter."},{"time":912480,"text":"Get involved;"},{"time":913720,"text":"don't sit on your couch and tell people\nwhat you think they should be doing."},{"time":917320,"text":"Go do it with us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":919840,"text":"MB: Do you guys want to add anything?"},{"time":922320,"text":"That's good? All right. So --"},{"time":924200,"text":"And I think that the joining something,"},{"time":926320,"text":"like if you feel like there's\nnot something where you are, start it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":929560,"text":"AG: Start it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":930800,"text":"MB: These conversations that we're having,"},{"time":932880,"text":"have those conversations\nwith somebody else."},{"time":935000,"text":"And then instead of just\nletting it be a talk that you had,"},{"time":937840,"text":"actually decide to start something."}]},{"cues":[{"time":939560,"text":"OT: That's right."}]},{"cues":[{"time":940840,"text":"MB: I mean, that's what you all did."},{"time":942579,"text":"You started something,\nand look what's happened."},{"time":944859,"text":"Thank you all so much\nfor being here with us today."}]},{"cues":[{"time":947800,"text":"OT: Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":949040,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}